snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Secret of the Mimic - PS5 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Five Nights at Freddy's: Secret of the Mimic - 6.13.2025

In Five Nights at Freddy's: Secret of the Mimic, navigate the shadowy Costume Manor and uncover the secrets of Edwin Murray's unfinished invention: the elusive and menacing Mimic animatronic.

Pre-order here: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10012344/
